## ğŸ“ˆ Key SQL Queries & Insights

- **Monthly Sales Revenue**
```sql
SELECT FORMAT(sale_date, 'yyyy-MM') AS sale_month, SUM(total_amount) AS revenue FROM sales GROUP BY FORMAT(sale_date, 'yyyy-MM');

